OL,3,CPoliticians warn of resistance to
OL,4,Cchange and 'gerrymandering' as
OL,5,Celection looms
OL,7,FThree outgoing Jersey politicians have
OL,8,Fwarned incoming candidates of the slow
OL,9,Fpace, lack of collaboration, and
OL,10,Fresistance to change.
OL,12,FAs residents head to the polls on
OL,13,FSunday 7 June, Deputies Moz Scott and
OL,14,FGeoff Southern and Connetable Phillip
OL,15,Fle Sueur were candid about their
OL,16,Fconcerns.
OL,18,FAll three politicians have chosen not
OL,19,Fto run for reelection and suggested
OL,20,Fthat they had not been able to deliver
OL,21,Fwhat they wanted to in government.
OL,26,@vD@Xrr
