CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1780423900
OL,3,CPoliticians warn of resistance to
OL,4,Cchange and 'gerrymandering' as
OL,5,Celection looms
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Channel, they said
OL,8,Fthat "resistance to change" and
OL,9,Fchanges to the electoral system were
OL,10,Fslowing down Jersey's potential, with
OL,11,Fone even claiming the return of
OL,12,FSenators amounts to "gerrymandering",
OL,13,Fdespite the returning race being an
OL,14,Fisland-wide mandate.
OL,16,FDeputy Scott was elected to the States
OL,17,Fas Deputy of St Brelade in 2022, and
OL,18,Fhas served for a single term.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1780423900
OL,3,CPoliticians warn of resistance to
OL,4,Cchange and 'gerrymandering' as
OL,5,Celection looms
OL,7,FShe served as Chair of the Economic
OL,8,Fand International Affairs Scrutiny
OL,9,FPanel for two years, and also the
OL,10,FAssistant Minister for External
OL,11,FRelations until February this year.
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV News, Deputy Scott
OL,14,Fsaid that she was frustrated by the
OL,15,Fslow pace of change, adding "a lot of
OL,16,Fthat is because of the way things are
OL,17,Forganised".
OL,19,FDeputy Scott added that
OL,20,F"personalities" within government
OL,21,Foften slowed down decision-making.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1780423900
OL,3,CPoliticians warn of resistance to
OL,4,Cchange and 'gerrymandering' as
OL,5,Celection looms
OL,7,F"There are senior officials who are
OL,8,Ftaking political positions, which I
OL,9,Freally don't feel is acceptable," she
OL,10,Fexplained.
OL,12,F"I have tried to bring measures and
OL,13,Fbring suggestions to deal (with
OL,14,Fgovernment) more efficiently, and they
OL,15,Fjust haven't been taken up.
OL,17,F"I think there is just a resistance to
OL,18,Fchange, even by those who stood on a
OL,19,Fmanifesto saying they wanted change."
OL,26,@uD@[pmvD@Kpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
