PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1780423900
OL,3,CPoliticians warn of resistance to
OL,4,Cchange and 'gerrymandering' as
OL,5,Celection looms
OL,7,FDeputy Geoff Southern also regretted
OL,8,Fthe lack of progress in parts of
OL,9,Fgovernment.
OL,11,FSouthern was first elected in 2002 as
OL,12,FDeputy of St Helier. He has been re-
OL,13,Felected as Deputy six times since and
OL,14,Fis currently the Vice Chair of the
OL,15,FMember of Economic and International
OL,16,FAffairs Scrutiny Panel.
OL,18,FThe outgoing politician says that the
OL,19,F"feeling that (government) was going
OL,20,Fnowhere" was among the reasons why he
OL,21,Fwanted to stand down.
OL,26,@{D@Opm{D@Zpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
