CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1780423900
OL,3,CPoliticians warn of resistance to
OL,4,Cchange and 'gerrymandering' as
OL,5,Celection looms
OL,7,F"Short-term (thinking) just rules the
OL,8,Froost," he told ITV News. "People do
OL,9,Fthings not for any particularly good
OL,10,Freasons, but because they can. It's
OL,11,Fnot good enough; we can do better."
OL,13,FHe was particularly critical of the
OL,14,Fdecision to bring back Senators.
OL,16,FThe role was scrapped in 2022 but will
OL,17,Freturn this year, replacing one deputy
OL,18,Fin each Parish. Deputies who voted for
OL,19,Fthe measure hope that it will restore
OL,20,Fan "island-wide mandate" to the States.
OL,26,@oD@MpmoD@Vpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
