CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1780423900
OL,3,CPoliticians warn of resistance to
OL,4,Cchange and 'gerrymandering' as
OL,5,Celection looms
OL,7,F"It's an absolute mistake and complete
OL,8,Fgerrymandering to get the right people
OL,9,Fin the right place," he said.
OL,11,FConnetable Phillip le Sueur had
OL,12,Fdifferent reasons for stepping down.
OL,14,F"To be perfectly honest, I'll be 73
OL,15,Fthis year," he said. "I think it's
OL,16,Ftime to step over, and let someone
OL,17,Fyoung and fitter take the helm."
OL,26,@sD@Err
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
