PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1780423900
OL,3,CPoliticians warn of resistance to
OL,4,Cchange and 'gerrymandering' as
OL,5,Celection looms
OL,7,FThe Connetable was first elected in
OL,8,FTrinity in 2014 and will have served
OL,9,Fthree full terms when he leaves the
OL,10,FAssembly this month.
OL,12,FCurrently the chair of the Planning
OL,13,FCommittee, he was previously also the
OL,14,FCommissioner for Jersey Overseas Aid
OL,15,FCommission.
OL,17,FLe Sueur also voiced concerns about
OL,18,Fthe tone of Jersey politics in recent
OL,19,Fyears. He observed that in his third
OL,20,Fand final term, politics had become
OL,21,F"more confrontational".
OL,26,@oD@Irr
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
