OL,3,CPoliticians warn of resistance to
OL,4,Cchange and 'gerrymandering' as
OL,5,Celection looms
OL,7,F"I don't think it bodes well for an
OL,8,Fassembly to get together and work
OL,9,Fcollaboratively", he said.
OL,11,F"The atmosphere in the coffee room
OL,12,Fsometimes has been a little bit
OL,13,Fdifficult, shall we say."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
